{
  "id": "adv_event_2309_01_03",
  "title": "日々募る焦り",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "……ふぅ、初回にしては順調に詰めることが出来たわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Whew‚ we managed to cover a lot of ground for our first session.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 5.7895236969,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "そう……ですね。確かに順調だと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes… You’re right‚ things are moving along smoothly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.9895236969,
      "endTime": 12.4495235443,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "でも……芽衣とすずがライバルなんですから\n今のうちに出来ることをもっともっとしておきたいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… Mei and Suzu are our rivals‚\nso I want us to do as much as we can now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.6561901252,
      "endTime": 19.7976865929,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "その気持ちも分かるけどもう二十一時を回ってるわよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand how you feel‚ but it’s already past 9 PM.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.9976864021,
      "endTime": 25.155759159800002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "後少しだけ！　芽衣とユニットを組んだ時に考えた\nけどやる余裕がなかったステップが何個かあるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just a little while longer! I thought of some steps when I was in a unit with Mei‚\nbut we didn’t have time to try them out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.3557591598,
      "endTime": 34.2808383148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうなのね。それなら次の練習ではそれを――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I see… Then during our next practice session――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.4675050577,
      "endTime": 39.7420173487,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "なるべく早く試した方がいいと思って\n今から一通りやってみませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think it’d be best if we tried them as soon as possible.\nWhy don’t we run through them now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.58868653,
      "endTime": 46.1486867588,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ！？　れ、怜ちゃん、明日も早朝から\n生放送があるし今日はこれくらいにしましょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh!? R-Rei! We have a live broadcast early tomorrow morning‚\nso how about we stop here for today?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.3353534064,
      "endTime": 53.7737434705,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "……あ、そうでした\nすみません、さすがに今日は厳しいですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ah‚ right.\nI’m sorry. It’s true that we can’t push ourselves too hard today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.967076556,
      "endTime": 62.7843781153,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "あんまり焦ってもしょうがないわよ\n今日だって番組収録を二つ終えてから練習してるんだし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s no need to be so impatient.\nWe’ve already done two program recordings today and we’re still practicing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.9910448392,
      "endTime": 69.9478021939,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "そう……ですよね。無理は怪我のもとですもんね\n分かりました、今日はこれくらいにしましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s… true. It’s not good to push ourselves too hard‚ we might get injured.\nI understand. We should stop for today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.1411352793,
      "endTime": 80.3033121744,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Several days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.1033121744,
      "endTime": 82.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "う～ん、どうしたものかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… What should I do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.1166485786,
      "endTime": 86.45533342360001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "（ユニットの活動を通じてもっと仲良くなって）\n（怜ちゃんの悩みが聞けたらと思ったんだけど）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I was hoping to get closer to Rei through our unit activities‚ ）\n（and maybe she’d open up to me about her worries‚）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.6019896109,
      "endTime": 95.6078626234,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "（怜ちゃんてば、やる気が凄過ぎて練習中に）\n（世間話をする余裕がまるでないのよね）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（but she’s so incredibly motivated that during practice）\n（there’s absolutely no time for idle chatter.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.8145294427,
      "endTime": 102.58169491279999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "（やる気があるのは凄くいいことだけど）\n（これじゃあ怜ちゃんと組んだ意味が……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（It’s great that she's so driven‚ ）\n（but at this rate‚ what was the point of us becoming a unit…?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.7816950082,
      "endTime": 109.2816948176,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さん？　そんなに考え込んでどうしたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san? You seem lost in thought. What’s wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.4216957967,
      "endTime": 117.1120599668,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "……怜ちゃん。私とこの後ご飯に行ってみるとか\nどうかな～……な～んて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Rei. Why don’t we have dinner together later?\nHow about it…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.3187264999,
      "endTime": 125.0215156158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "え？　ご飯ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Dinner?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.2348490636,
      "endTime": 129.5191348951,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あはは、そうよね、いきなりは厳しいわよね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ ahaha. You’re right‚ it’s a bit much to ask out of the blue!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.7258015712,
      "endTime": 135.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、それは別に構わないんですけど……でも\n今日はサニピ全員でご飯を食べる約束じゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ it’s not that I mind… But\ndidn’t we promise to have dinner with everyone from Sunny Peace today?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.7058034818,
      "endTime": 145.1199983518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "あ……そうだったわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… That’s right.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.3199981611,
      "endTime": 148.2666687012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "それに、私と遙子さんが炊事当番ですよ\nもう少ししたら、買い出しに出掛けないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And‚ you and I are in charge of cooking tonight.\nWe’ll have to go shopping soon.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.548260371,
      "endTime": 156.95984789539997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "それよ、それだわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s it‚ that’s it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.1465147337,
      "endTime": 159.7843831858,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 161.041049862
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "さあ、買い出し頑張るぞ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ let’s do our best with grocery shopping~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.091049862,
      "endTime": 165.0847687722,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "お、お～……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "O-oh~…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.298102053,
      "endTime": 169.3647584517,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 169.5514250993
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03-hrk015.m4a",
      "text": "（私がカートを押して、怜ちゃんが隣に並ぶ……）\n（これは車で言うところの運転席と助手席の関係！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I’m pushing the cart‚ and Rei is walking next to me…）\n（This is just like being the driver and the passenger in a car!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.5514250993,
      "endTime": 178.733035016,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_03-hrk016.m4a",
      "text": "（会話が弾みやすい車内と同じ状況なら……）\n（怜ちゃんとの会話も盛り上がること間違いなしよね！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（If it’s the same as being in a car‚ where conversations flow easily…）\n（I’m sure I’ll be able to have a good chat with Rei!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 178.919701759,
      "endTime": 185.86237763559998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
